caption: Very impressed with the pasta specials at lunch.  The perfectly cooked asparagus was just what I needed.  I've eaten at every restaurant in Kingman and these have been the only fresh vegetables I've had.  In my book, iceberg lettuce and orange tomatoes don't cut it.
